Comment produire l'archetype de technologyAdapter
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

  Respecter les pré-requis {{pre_requis.html}}

  Voir Aussi

  * {{http://maven.apache.org/archetype/maven-archetype-plugin/usage.html}}

  * {{http://maven.apache.org/guides/introduction/introduction-to-archetypes.html}}


On y va
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* tester l'archetype

+------------------------------------------------------------------------+
  mvn verify
+------------------------------------------------------------------------+

* fabriquer la documentation

+------------------------------------------------------------------------+
  mvn site ; firefox  file://${PWD}/target/site/fr/index.html
+------------------------------------------------------------------------+

* installer en local d'archetype

+------------------------------------------------------------------------+
  mvn install
+------------------------------------------------------------------------+

** publier l'archetype sur le dépot binaire

+------------------------------------------------------------------------+
  mvn deploy
+------------------------------------------------------------------------+

